---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import ProfileCard from "../components/ProfileCard.astro";
---
<Base title="Aditya Wagh">
  <section class="intro-section">
    <div class="mb-6 md:float-left md:mr-8 md:mb-3 md:mt-2">
      <ProfileCard />
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">Hi, I'm Aditya Wagh</h1>

      <p>
        I'm an AI Research Engineer based in London, specializing in robotics and computer vision. I currently
        work at <a href="https://neuracore.com">Neuracore</a>, a company founded by
        <a href="https://stepjam.github.io/">Stephen James</a> — one of the pioneers of the field — where I work across
        the complete Physical AI and robot learning lifecycle, spanning data collection and training all the way to
        ML inference and deployment.
      </p>

      <p>
        I did my master's at <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_York_University">NYU</a> and my bachelor's at
        <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BITS_Pilani">BITS Pilani</a>, both in electrical engineering, with a
        focus on machine learning, computer vision, and robotics. Before Neuracore, I worked on Machine Learning based
        <a href="https://github.com/adityamwagh/SuperSLAM">SLAM</a> (Simultaneous Localization and Mapping) at NYU's
        <a href="https://ai4ce.github.io/">AI4CE lab</a>, advised by
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&user=YeG8ZM0AAAAJ">Dr. Chen Feng</a>, Founding Co-Director
        of the NYU <a href="https://robotics.engineering.nyu.edu/">Center for Robotics and Embodied Intelligence</a> (CREO).
      </p>

      <p>
        My interests span computer vision, robot learning, world models, self-driving, and autonomy, and I'm always open
        to research collaborations and roles in these areas. Outside work, I read widely — programming languages, systems and
        performance engineering, and ML systems, along with public policy, history, and psychology. If any of this
        resonates, let's connect — reach me on <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adityamwagh">LinkedIn</a>, by
        <a href="mailto:adityamwagh@outlook.com">email</a>, or on
        <a href="https://twitter.com/adityamwagh">X/Twitter</a> (open DMs).
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="clear-both"></div>
  </section>
</Base>
